Rating: 4
I too had a bunch of summer squash on hand and wanted to not only use it but get my 6 1/2 year old to eat some vegetables. This recipe is FANTASTIC! I used ground turkey instead of beef. My 6 1/2 yr old ate the whole thing and asked for me. He had no clue there was anything healthy in this sloppy joe. Now I know what to do with all the summer squash we get!

Rating: 4
I made this recipe because I had a bunch of summer squash on hand and wanted to try something different... it was outstanding! It took no time to prepare and was delightful to eat. We used soy fake-meat instead of turkey or beef, but I'm sure it would've been equally delicious with real meat. Give it a try!